<tr id="L494"><td><a href="#L494">494</a></td><td>LAVELLE:  Thanks. It just don't feel right. For all I know, she was going to get the promotion instead of me.</td></tr>

<tr id="L495"><td><a href="#L495">495</a></td><td>BEN:  You shouldn't feel that way, Sam.</td></tr>

